data.description: Welcome to 214 San Marcos Dr. in the River Farms Subdivision, zoned to the highly acclaimed Barbers Hill Independent School District. The easily maintained landscaping invites you into the home with high ceilings and a bedroom with bathroom near the entry. French doors for your office are off the kitchen which is open to the dining room and living room. The expansive ceilings make the room feel huge and is ready for your artwork. The large kitchen island offers plenty of cabinets and counter space and is perfect for entertaining. The primary suite is secluded so offers privacy with this split floor plan. Upstairs you will find two additional large bedrooms, bathroom, game room, and a third bedroom that can double as a media room. This home is conveniently located near Highway 99 & I10. Call for your showing today!
